songs.title: Another Day
songs.lyrics:
[Chorus]
You`re not ready, to spend the night with me
There's always another day
Rainin’ on my parade
It seem like she scared
What I wanna do to you, I wanna go to bed
So scared, damn, baby, whoa (Man)
There's always another day

[Verse]
There's always another day
I’ma put on Marvin Gaye
I push the button away, for you, oh yeah
Stop me when I'm getting boring
I'm your little sexaholic, all day
Wake up with me in the morning and say
You don't regret it baby, yeah, yeah
All I gotta prove to you
What I gotta do to you
I just don't think you're ready

[Chorus]
You`re not ready, to spend the night with me
There's always another day
Rainin' on my parade
It seem like she scared
What I wanna do to you, I wanna go to bed
So scared, damn, baby, whoa (Man)
There’s always another day
